The paper proposes a method for missing information reconstruction in remote sensing images using a deep convolutional neural network. This involves processing spatial, temporal, and spectral data, which suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), graphics (cs.GR), or information theory (cs.IT). However, given the focus on image processing and deep learning, cs.CV and cs.LG are the most likely categories.
